OL,3,CInmates who murdered child killer will
OL,4,Cnever be released
OL,6,FThree prisoners have been given whole
OL,7,Flife sentences for murdering a child
OL,8,Fkiller in his cell.
OL,10,FConvicted killers Mark Fellows, 45,
OL,11,FLee Newell, 57, and David Taylor, 64,
OL,12,Fstabbed Kyle Bevan to death at high-
OL,13,Fsecurity HMP Wakefield in West
OL,14,FYorkshire last November.
OL,16,FThey then put him in bed and left him
OL,17,Fto bleed out.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
