FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781892673
OL,3,CInmates who murdered child killer will
OL,4,Cnever be released
OL,6,FFellows and Newell were already
OL,7,Fserving whole life orders when they
OL,8,Fkilled Bevan, meaning they would never
OL,9,Fhave been released in any case.
OL,11,FThe judge, Mrs Justice McGowan,
OL,12,Fimposed "new and separate" whole life
OL,13,Forders on both of them for Bevan's
OL,14,Fmurder.
OL,16,FTaylor was given a whole life order
OL,17,Ffor Bevan's death, on top of offences
OL,18,Fhe had been convicted of.
OL,26,@tD@IOUtD@ZO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
