CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781892673
OL,3,CInmates who murdered child killer will
OL,4,Cnever be released
OL,6,FHe was on remand for the murder of
OL,7,Fmissing 24-year-old Alisha Apostoloff-
OL,8,FBoyarin ` a vulnerable woman he was in
OL,9,Fa relationship with but had grown
OL,10,Ftired of ` and the attempted murder of
OL,11,Fa police officer in an interview room
OL,12,Fat another high-security jail.
OL,14,FMrs Justice McGowan jailed Taylor for
OL,15,Flife with a minimum term of 20 years
OL,16,Ffor Ms Apostoloff-Boyarin's murder and
OL,17,Fhanded him a 30-year sentence for the
OL,18,Fattempted murder of the officer.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
