OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781892673
OL,3,CInmates who murdered child killer will
OL,4,Cnever be released
OL,6,FShe then imposed a whole life order
OL,7,Ffor the death of Bevan, as it was a
OL,8,Fsecond offence of murder.
OL,10,FBevan, 33, was serving a life sentence
OL,11,Fwith a minimum tariff of 28 years for
OL,12,Fmurdering his partner's two-year-old
OL,13,Fdaughter, Lola James, in
OL,14,FHaverfordwest, Pembrokeshire, in 2020.
OL,16,FAfter thanking the trial jurors who
OL,17,Fhad attended the sentencing hearing,
OL,18,Fthe judge said: "I've never had to
OL,19,Fsentence someone for a third murder,
OL,20,Fand in two of these defendants' cases
OL,21,Fthat's what just happened."
OL,26,@zD@QOU}D@[O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
