PN,33305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781892673
OL,3,CInmates who murdered child killer will
OL,4,Cnever be released
OL,6,FFellows was the only one of the three
OL,7,Fto attend court for the hearing, with
OL,8,FNewell and Taylor joining by video-
OL,9,Flink from prison.
OL,11,FThe court heard Newell was first
OL,12,Fjailed for murder in 1989 after
OL,13,Fstrangling his female neighbour, who
OL,14,Fwas in her 50s at the time, after she
OL,15,Frefused to give him money.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781892673
OL,3,CInmates who murdered child killer will
OL,4,Cnever be released
OL,6,FHe was then given a whole life order
OL,7,Fin 2013 after strangling a prisoner
OL,8,Fwho murdered a child and leaving him
OL,9,Fin his bed, with "a chilling
OL,10,Fsimilarity to... the circumstances of
OL,11,FKyle Bevan's death".
OL,13,FNewell lost an eye in a prison yard
OL,14,Fattack in 2014, for which he was later
OL,15,Fawarded #85,000 in damages.
OL,17,FFellows, a hitman known as "the
OL,18,FWakefield Dexter", had committed two
OL,19,Fgangland murders and was given a whole
OL,20,Flife term in 2019.
OL,26,@qD@ROUsD@SO]yD@\OUzD@QO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781892673
OL,3,CInmates who murdered child killer will
OL,4,Cnever be released
OL,6,FHe had formally applied to move from
OL,7,FWakefield not long before Bevan's
OL,8,Fkilling because of his dissatisfaction
OL,9,Fwith the regime there.
OL,11,FTaylor had recently been transferred
OL,12,Fto Wakefield.
OL,14,FThe court heard Taylor boasted about
OL,15,Fhis ability to make makeshift weapons
OL,16,F"out of all sorts", and after Bevan's
OL,17,Fdeath some were found in a bottle of
OL,18,Fchilli sauce in his cell, although
OL,19,Fthey could not be matched to the fatal
OL,20,Fattack.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@RO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781892673
OL,3,CInmates who murdered child killer will
OL,4,Cnever be released
OL,6,FWhen Taylor appeared on video-link for
OL,7,Fhearings before the jury was sworn in,
OL,8,Fhe was escorted into a room at Full
OL,9,FSutton prison, near York, by a number
OL,10,Fof officers in full riot gear.
OL,12,FThey had to remove two sets of
OL,13,Fhandcuffs from him before he was
OL,14,Fallowed to sit and listen to lawyers
OL,15,Fdiscuss fears over the danger he posed.
OL,17,FThe judge was told there had been
OL,18,Fconcerns from prison authorities that
OL,19,FTaylor had somehow managed to secrete
OL,20,Fa weapon in his body ` for some weeks
OL,21,F` but this could not be found.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
