FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1781892673
OL,3,CInmates who murdered child killer will
OL,4,Cnever be released
OL,6,FThe judge was also told prison
OL,7,Fauthorities wanted all three
OL,8,Fdefendants to be handcuffed if they
OL,9,Fgave evidence in the witness box but,
OL,10,Fin the end, none of them took to the
OL,11,Fstand.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/9
